T1  - EXPLAINING THE SPREAD OF TEMPORARY JOBS AND ITS IMPACT ON LABOR TURNOVER
AU  - Cahuc, Pierre
AU  - Charlot, Olivier
AU  - Malherbet, Franck
Y1  - 2016/05/01
PY  - 2016
DA  - 2016/05/01
