T1  - MODELING THE EVOLUTION OF EXPECTATIONS AND UNCERTAINTY IN GENERAL EQUILIBRIUM
AU  - Bianchi, Francesco
AU  - Melosi, Leonardo
Y1  - 2016/05/01
PY  - 2016
DA  - 2016/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12174
T2  - International Economic Review
